Package com.team7.cmput301.android.theirisproject.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddBodyPhotoController  
    AddPatientController
    AddPatientController is responsible for executing AddPatientTask which will update the given Care Provider and corresponding Patient to hold each other's IDs in the database
    AddProblemController
    AddProblemController has methods to allow our AddProblemActivity to interact with the database by POST requesting new problems to it
    AddRecordController
    AddRecordController handles the models within the AddRecordActivity form.
    BodyPhotoListController
    BodyPhotoListController handles the modifications and queries of body photos to be displayed on BodyPhotoListActivity
    DeleteProblemController
    DeleteProblemController has methods to allow DeleteProblemActivity to interact with the database to delete problems.
    EditProblemController
    Controller that submits the edited problem to the database Called from EditProblemActivity
    EditProfileController
    EditProfileController is used by EditProfileActivity to update the User's profile into the DB
    EditRecordController
    Controller for editing a Record
    GetAllGeoLocationsController
    AllGeolocationsController collects all record's geolocations and record titles.
    IrisController<M>
    A type of controller that is used by an IrisActivity to manage a Model object.
    LoginController
    LoginController helps the activity interact with the database by separating its concern of handling the asynchronous calls to authenticate fields
    PatientListController
    PatientListController is responsible for getting a Care Provider's list of Patients from the database
    ProblemController
    Controller that gets the problem from the database Called from ViewProblemActivity
    ProblemListController
    ProblemListController allows the Activity/Model to interact with each other without explicitly mutating each other.
    RecordController
    RecordController allows communication between the Record Model and the Record Activity
    RecordListController
    Controller for RecordListActivity
    RecordPhotoListController
    RecordPhotoListController's main purpose is to return a list of all record photos associated with a problem
    RegisterController
    Controller for making a new User
    SearchController
    SearchController handles the input coming from activity to search for results
